###BEGIN_avgCol###
Usage: avgCol dataset

Description:
	The avgCol function calculates the mean of the numerical values in each column. Missing values will be excluded. Non-numeric text must be removed first.

Arguments:
	dataset	ex: test3.stat	Dataset to be processed.

Example:
	avgCol test3.stat 
##END_avgCol##


